This directory contains python library used by qualimetrics.


--  SQLAlchemy  --

What for

    Use for interracting with the database with orm system management.


How to install
    
    $ pip install --no-install SQLAlchemy -d path/to/directory/for/lib/source
    $ export PYHTONUSERBASE=/path/to/install/dir/
    --> this step allow .pth file to work in the install directory. This kind
    of file is used for the installation of python package
    $ python setup.py --without-cextensions install --user
    --> install the package in python use base directory, set previously

    --> if you get this error:
        [Errno 2] No such file or directory:
        '/path/to/instal/dir/lib/python2.7/site-packages/test-easy-install-28362.write-test
    --> create recursively directories: 'lib/python2.7/site-packagesand/' then
        try again

